Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The history of games can be traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the way to Ancient Egypt 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These ancient games decided the fate of the citizens and the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were called the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the time where a boy has solved the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and released the Dark Games has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy with both a heart of light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People refer to him as Yuugiou: The Game King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,136)}Friendship Power!\N Barbarian #1 & #2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find that damn Mokuba anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He surely was taken to Pegasus's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to get in Pegasus's castle is collecting ten star chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(403,412)}Jounouchi - 2 Star chips\NYugi - 6 Star chips
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found some cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You play Duel Monsters too, Honda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I became interested in it, so I bought some cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then brought them with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbarian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I saw something like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number one and number two? Having them both would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's a pain to have this card, but I'll keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, isn't it? You won't use it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... can't help it. I'll lend this card for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... It's a great duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot number one and idiot number two, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Queens, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triangle Ecstasy Spark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It's my win. Leave your star chips and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow this is boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it! How could I lose to someone like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally found ya, Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Dinosaur Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't forget what happened on da ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're talking about that, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge ya to a new match here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in men that already have lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got the strength of da National Championship, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already got five star chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eight star chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you understand? I only need two star chips to get in Pegasus's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I've already decided the opponent that will give me the remaining star chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} gonna beat 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} win against {\i1}Yugi{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll duel you. But there's one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These people over there don't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seem very strong but they are suitable to Jounouchi, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Haga looked weak but was really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but I don't think that there's someone in this island weaker than Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerks! You've been laughing at me for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This loud voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are tagging along with each other, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you ducks in a former life?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ducks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, don't you think it's troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Jounouchi weren't slowing you down, you would already be at Pegasus's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here now to fight you.\N My target is Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:06:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time I lost to you, but this time my servant will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Yugi, Jounouchi-han.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinosaur Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Mai Kujaku's servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little envious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What foolishness are you saying?! Hurry up and refuse her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, you'll run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This's good. I should be {\b0}grateful{\b1} to Mai Kujaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually {\b0}I{\b1} want revenge, but that would be immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I defeat Ryuzaki after Jounouchi loses to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then it would be like I defeated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This woman... is doing this because she lost to Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But just watch! This time again, with Yugi's support...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Yeah! This duel will have a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The public can't give advice to the duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone gives advice, the duel won't be considered as a real one, right, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay with this condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm really reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose my star chips in this duel, I'll be forced off of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I want to win with my own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to always be depending on Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were in the city's tournament best eight, you can't win against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. He's a little out of himself now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget what he said about the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask for your opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What that woman said is true. Surely if I wasn't here, Yugi would already be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, I never thought that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't even defend myself, it would be better for me to lose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard... think a little about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, what will happen to your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not cheer for an idiot like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do? If you want to give up, we can cancel this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I will accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, in this duel, don't give me any advice, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having to fight without Yugi's advice leaves me a bit scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Servant, you have to win, or you won't receive your reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... what reward will you receive if you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't yer business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many star chips will you bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, two! All my star chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! My field is wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is grassland.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that he was a competitor in the national tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his dinosaur cards are strong....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I too have my powerful combo that defeated Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Time Magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Baby Dragon can transform into the powerful Thousand Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, I'll leave Jounouchi-kun with you. I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already drew Baby Dragon and the Time Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well... it's alright. Even without Yugi, I already won this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Dragon in defense mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, play a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the next turn, my killer combo will destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-headed King Rex in attack mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Rex destroyed Baby Dragon with one movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Baby Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya freakin' {\i1}numb{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone that would start with a monster in defense mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why dont'cha use yer head a little? Yer head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, it's useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AS expected from an amateur...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, his plan to use Time Magician
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to transform Baby Dragon into Thousand Dragon has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, draw and play the next card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter what card it is, my dinosaur card will destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really looks powerful, but I have some powerful cards in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Leogun! Defeat King Rex!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya really {\i1}are{\i0} numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:12:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My King Rex gets stronger with da wasteland field power source! It receives a power up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinosaur Foot Stomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My true objective is ta defeat Mai Kujaku, so I gotta hurry an' beat Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll leave as it is. Hurry up and play your next card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My field is grassland... It must favor my knight and warrior cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Axe Raider! With the field power source he powers up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I play this card! Sword Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Tail Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. Can't I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing Jounouchi? Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Honda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised I wouldn't give any advice, so whether I'm there or not it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, how can you say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whether I'm there or not it's the same".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong. You don't have to keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't help him, then what you have is not a true friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until this duel's finished, I won't talk to Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Jounouchi-kun believes that if he can win by his own power,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-chan can do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun probably was worried when he accepted the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this battle of his until the end. It's the best way to show your friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Jounouchi-kun understands your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn! Where are you, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm still counting on Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to win with my own power! I decided to do that for Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my hand, I don't have any card that can beat his dinosaur card...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This... Time Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't know any other way to use it, but to create the Thousand Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What other power does it have?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, I'll set this card in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That card... I have no doubts that it is the Time Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is, without a doubt, the Time Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, an amateur like him can't use it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time Magician is a card that possesses a great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Harpie Ladies were defeated by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put a monster in defense mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever card it is, it'll be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megasaurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megasaurus's charge attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you already give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, you played a powerful card...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Flame Swordsman's attack power is less than the Megasaurus'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megasaurus! Charge Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning Sword of Fighting Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? My Megasaurus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Swordsman is a fire monster... That happens to be dinosaurs' weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it was luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, dinosaur bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flame Swordsman... Being a fire monster really sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strong! Jounouchi will win! He'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the game has turned to my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:17:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me! I still have rare cards in my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear! Evil Night Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This's a premium-card given to the ones who passed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the second round in the national tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! You'll always be a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nightmare Shadow Sonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have any card that can beat that powerful monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is... Honda's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You... want to take us alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People like you that bully the weak really piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll beat you so you can't even stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! Are you alright, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Coming here alone was madness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was my fight! I could've taken them on alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never noticed before but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honda... you always have been by my side since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! If I'm not around, he can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Honda! Let's fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! Here's the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nightmare Shadow Sonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Barbarian Number 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What happened? The Shadow Sonic was reflected!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Barbarian Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda's card helped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! When these monsters are together on the field, they help each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun's friendship saved Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now, let's continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight together, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well... no problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be happy while ya still can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(137,52)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friendship power has manifested and saved Jounouchi from a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the arrival of Dinosaur Ryuzaki's best monster, he will be in a second pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notice it, Jounouchi! What can change everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a new person joins us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Bakura-kun? I {\i1}knew{\i0} you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Dark Fire! Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:21:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:22:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
